{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, they'll show me how to get back to the jail where I am.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I talked to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out from them the story about-- I didn't tell them that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't want to burden them with keeping secrets, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they told me that, again, no-- no-- no killing, no murders, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's bad enough that they have to, you know, sort of labor camps, and things were much worse.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're now much better, and they are getting better and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got interrogated by a-- they called him prosecutor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But actually, he was like a-- no, he was actually like an investigative judge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the name-- investigative judge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they brought you to him, and I would-- he was very friendly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and I could see that things will end up good for me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he was kind of asking me questions in a way where he was tipping me of what answers I should give so that it will help me to get released from jail.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he would kind of, you know, I don't remember the details.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I knew right there and then that I'm-- I'm in good shape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, my father came back from the interrogation, tell me the same story.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He believed that I'm a Pole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He believed my father was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He believed my father his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He believed me his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't question, didn't interrogate, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He kind of tried to help, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
